            <h4 class="text-secondary">Folder System</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>In the side menu is a folders option that will show a new side menu page, containing all available folders and an add folder button at the bottom.</li>
                <li>One of these available folders can be selected at a time and if selected, all receipts logged after will be added to this folder.</li>
